data.description:
Hard to find beautiful country home OUTSIDE of city limits, NO HOA, NO CITY TAXES in Burleson ISD under $400k! 4-2-2 with just under an acre of land has the versatility for a small or large family inside and out! Large open-concept living and kitchen area great for entertaining, exceptionally large yard with plenty of space, fruit-bearing pear, and peach trees, sectioned with plenty of space for animals, gardens, or a large workshop or barn. Lots of storage space inside home and large insulated, w electricity and AC shed-workshop. On a quiet private drive, mature cedar trees outlining the front of the property, overlooking neighboring pastures, a peaceful semi-secluded home just minutes away from city amenities.  
Owners have updated: HVAC system, water heater in 2021, stainless steel kitchen appliances <5 years old, roof was replaced in 2019, wood flooring less than a year old, newly updated master bathroom, electrical panel 2023. The property is fenced. IMAGES INCLUDE MAP w DRIVE.
